{
  "stem": "14463.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his group was one of the first to break through in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, actually, he was killed in the Reichstag, and the whole city was weeping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is what I remember in Kyzylorda, this one thing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Next thing what I remember Kyzylorda is this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working on the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], you know, on the loom, and my mother was going to the market and she was also buying a bit of rice and selling a bit of rice to make a bit of money, you know, when the war is finished, that way when we go home we'll have something to start with, right?",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day she comes home and she said to me, there's a man I met in the market, a Jewish man I met in the market, and he's giving me a tremendous good rate to buy [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was American gold dollars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, she got all together all the money which she had at home, and she went to a couple of the neighbors to borrow some more money and she went to the market.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She came to the market and she came home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was very happy that she's such a good deal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the money was in a tube.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she-- I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She pulls out the tube on a table there, you know,a little table.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the first three was gold coins and the rest was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I knew that there's a train going to Tashkent and I'll catch the fellow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, how does he look?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she described him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I run to the train, and I felt this, that this is the fellow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said to him in Hebrew, I said, [SPEAKING HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, you'll die together with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
